story.title: CPS Public Hearing: Chicago Vocational Career Academy OSI Turnaround
story.description: A hearing for the proposed Reconstitution/Turnaround of Chicago Vocational Career Academy High School. The turnaround would be run by CPS OSI (Office of School Improvement). Held in the board room of the Chicago Public Schools administration building. Friday, February 3rd, 2012 5:30 - 7:30 PM

author.name: Josh Kalov
author.bio: Fan of education, politics, better government, open source software, sports, & most things peanut butter related.
